{
  "name": "01 · Webhook hello-world",
  "meta": {
    "_litePackNote": "Lite Pack 第 1 個工作流。最簡單驗證流程：Webhook 收到 GET 請求 → 回應 JSON。學員可拿來驗證 webhook 路徑、Make HTTP 整合、Quick Tunnel 連通。"
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## #1 Webhook hello-world\n\n**目的**：驗證 n8n 能接收外部 GET 請求。\n\n**測試方法**：\n1. 點下方紫色 Execute workflow\n2. Webhook 節點變藍色「Listening for test event」\n3. 瀏覽器打 http://localhost:5678/webhook-test/lite-hello （10 秒內）\n4. 預期看到 {\"message\": \"hello from lite pack\"}\n\n**改造方向**：\n- 改 Method 為 POST 收 body\n- Set 節點加更多回應欄位\n- 接 Telegram 節點轉發訊息",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 320
      },
      "id": "sticky-01",
      "name": "📌 使用說明",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-200, 0]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "GET",
        "path": "lite-hello",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-01",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 300],
      "webhookId": "lite-hello-webhook-id"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "msg-01",
              "name": "message",
              "value": "hello from lite pack",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "ts-01",
              "name": "timestamp",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "method-01",
              "name": "received_method",
              "value": "={{ $json.headers['x-real-ip'] || $json.headers.host || 'unknown' }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "set-01",
      "name": "Set: 回應內容",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [460, 300]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
